data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of NE Cape Coral! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence with a den is the epitome of comfortable, eco-friendly, and peaceful living. The property boasts several standout features, including solar panels that will be fully paid off at closing, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings for years to come. The kitchen features sleek appliances, plenty of counter space, and a breakfast bar, making it a chef's delight. The generous master suite is a true retreat, offering a walk-in closet and a private en-suite bathroom. Nestled in a tranquil and well-maintained neighborhood, this home provides a peaceful haven for you and your family.  Seller will contribute up to 10K towards closing costs. Schedule a viewing and make this house your own!
